"..#.",
"...."}</pre></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr><td class="statText"><pre>Returns: 1</pre></td></tr><tr><td class="statText"><table><tr><td colspan="2" class="statText">Move either piece horizontally (-1 point), then jump vertically (+2 points).</td></tr></table></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr><td align="center" nowrap class="statText">1)</td><td class="statText"></td></tr><tr><td class="statText">    </td><td class="statText"><table><tr><td class="statText"><table><tr><td class="statText"><pre>{
